comments: White (SAS) briefly places his hands to Bertans' (WAS) chest as Bertans is attempting to move over the screen, but immediately slides his hands off.
Bryant (WAS) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to White (SAS).
White (SAS) moves alongside of Beal (WAS) and does not deliver body contact during the driving shot attempt.  White avoids making contact with Beal's arm when he attempts to block the shot.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Beal (WAS).
Bryant (WAS) makes incidental  contact with DeRozan's (SAS) arm after the jump shot has been released.
Bryant (WAS) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to White (SAS).
White (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Beal (WAS).
Bryant (WAS) plants his right foot on the ground and firms up while setting the pick on Forbes (SAS).
Forbes (SAS) jumps legally alongside of Smith (WAS) and as he swipes at the ball in an attempt to block the shot, he does not make contact with Smith's arm.
Bertans (WAS) cleanly blocks Forbes (SAS) driving shot attempt.
Bertans (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Forbes (SAS).
White (SAS) jumps into Beal (WAS) and delivers body contact that affects Beal's SQBR.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Beal (WAS).
Bryant (WAS) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) shot attempt at the rim.
Murray (SAS) legally defends Beal's (WAS) driving shot attempt with his left arm collapsed against his body and his right arm vertical, absorbing the contact from Beal.

White (SAS) legally contests Beal's (WAS) driving shot attempt, jumping vertically and absorbing the contact from Beal. When White swipes down at the ball attempting to block the shot, he does not make contact with Beal's arm.
